      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Ready to hit the road without breaking the bank? This solid, dependable vehicle is priced to offer real value for the savvy shopper! It's in fair condition \u2014 you'll notice some wear and tear from years of use, including minor cosmetic blemishes and the typical signs of a well-lived life on the road, but it runs and gets you where you need to go. If you're looking for reliable everyday transportation at an accessible price point, this could be just the right fit for you!",
