    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Dependable & Well-Kept \u2014 A Smart Buy for Everyday Driving! This used car is in good condition and ready to hit the road with you! The exterior shows the kind of minor wear you'd expect from a well-loved vehicle, but it still presents nicely and turns heads. Under the hood, everything runs smoothly and reliably \u2014 this is a car you can count on for your daily commute or weekend adventures. The interior is comfortable and well-maintained, with normal signs of use that keep it feeling lived-in without being worn out. If you're after a solid, honest vehicle at a fair price, this one is well worth your time!",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
