      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $17,500, a price that honestly reflects its fair overall condition. The exterior shows visible wear beyond normal use \u2014 expect multiple scratches, some paint fading, and possibly minor dents or dings. The interior shows signs of regular use with worn upholstery and some scuffs on trim surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for basic transportation at an honest price, with the understanding that cosmetic imperfections are part of the package.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle in truly mint condition \u2014 one of the best examples you'll find anywhere on the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, showcasing a deep, rich paint finish with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks. The body panels are perfectly aligned, and every trim piece, seal, and chrome accent is in excellent shape. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells nearly new \u2014 the seats show no wear, the dashboard and door panels are free of cracks or fading, and all controls and displays function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with impressive smoothness and responsiveness. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in top working order. This vehicle has clearly been cared for with exceptional diligence, and a pre-purchase inspection will confirm everything described here. If you're looking for a used car that delivers a like-new experience without the new-car price tag, this is it.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Solid Driver at a Fair Price \u2014 Honest Value Here!** Looking for a dependable ride without breaking the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's fully drivable and gets the job done, though it does show its age with some visible cosmetic wear and minor imperfections you'd expect from a used car with history. Mechanically it's functional, but a savvy buyer should expect that some attention or routine maintenance may be needed down the road. If you want a real, usable vehicle at an honest price, this one deserves a look! Come see it in person and judge for yourself.",
