    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in fair shape and represents a solid opportunity for a buyer looking for a reliable daily driver or a solid used vehicle without the premium of a mint or good condition car. The car runs and drives, and while it shows its age with some cosmetic wear \u2014 think minor dents, surface scratches, and interior wear consistent with regular use \u2014 there are no major mechanical failures that would prevent safe, everyday operation. You can expect some items that may benefit from attention over time, such as minor maintenance items or cosmetic touch-ups, but nothing that should alarm a reasonably handy buyer or a good mechanic. Overall, this is an honest, functional vehicle priced fairly for what it is \u2014 a used car in fair condition that still has plenty of life left with reasonable care.",
